::DarkMouse::

She looked at Scorponok for a moment with a shocked look on her 
face. "Silly Mouse? Be Gone?"
She couldn't believe what her ears were telling her.  He said that to 
her? The one bot whom she would have sold her spark to save called 
her a silly mouse?! The one bot whom she had spend sleepless nights 
worrying over? The same bot who she cared for more than her own life? 
And he called her a silly mouse? She ran to her room and slammed the 
door.  "How dare he call me a silly mouse. After all that I did for 
him! After I let him take the credit for building the base? After 
looking out for him! He called me a Silly Mouse and tells me to Be 
Gone!" She flopped on her bed and cried.  She felt her spark 
breaking.
